2026-05-02  added  server/assets/captcha/DejaVuSans.ttf
            sha256   7da195a74c55bef988d0d48f9508bd5d849425c1770dba5d7bfc6ce9ed848954
            source   DejaVu Fonts 2.37, https://sourceforge.net/projects/dejavu/files/dejavu/2.37/
