            license  Bitstream Vera Fonts License + DejaVu Fonts License (permissive,
                     bundled in dejavu-fonts-ttf-2.37/LICENSE inside the upstream archive)
            purpose  Digit-pad renderer for the M1 captcha pipeline (`image` + `ab_glyph`).
